# Feature Walkthrough: PDF Analysis + Message Editing

## 1. PDF Upload & Analysis

### How it works

The chatbot now handles PDFs through a **2-stage pipeline**:

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User uploads PDF] --> B[Frontend detects .pdf attachment]
    B --> C[Fetch blob → POST /api/chat/analyze-pdf/]
    C --> D{pdfplumber extracts text?}
    D -- Yes, text found --> E[_summarize_text via llama-3.3-70b-versatile]
    D -- No, image-based PDF --> F[pymupdf renders pages as PNG at 150 DPI]
    F --> G[Base64 encode images]
    G --> H[_summarize_images via llama-4-scout vision model]
    E --> I[Return summary + metadata]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Save to ChatSession & ChatMessage in DB]
    J --> K[Frontend shows PDF Summary bubble]
```

### Backend ([rag/views.py](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/NEH/BTECH_CE/SEM%20VI/FarmEasy/2526_sdp8_onlineFarmerEducationAndComplaintSolvingPlatform/backend/rag/views.py))

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [_summarize_text()](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/NEH/BTECH_CE/SEM%20VI/FarmEasy/2526_sdp8_onlineFarmerEducationAndComplaintSolvingPlatform/backend/rag/views.py#85-102) | Groq `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` — for text PDFs |
| [_summarize_images()](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/NEH/BTECH_CE/SEM%20VI/FarmEasy/2526_sdp8_onlineFarmerEducationAndComplaintSolvingPlatform/backend/rag/views.py#104-138) | Groq `meta-llama/llama-4-scout-17b-16e-instruct` (vision) — for image PDFs |
| [analyze_pdf()](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/NEH/BTECH_CE/SEM%20VI/FarmEasy/2526_sdp8_onlineFarmerEducationAndComplaintSolvingPlatform/backend/rag/views.py#143-241) | Orchestrates: try pdfplumber → fallback to pymupdf + vision |

**Stage 1 — Text extraction** (`pdfplumber`):
- Reads all pages, strips text
- Truncates at 12,000 chars if too large
- Sends to `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` with agricultural analyst system prompt

**Stage 2 — Image OCR** (only if Stage 1 yields no text):
- Opens PDF via `fitz.open()` (PyMuPDF)
- Renders up to 10 pages as PNG at 150 DPI
- Base64-encodes each PNG
- Sends all images + instruction to Groq vision model
- `used_ocr: true` is returned in the response

### Frontend ([Chatbot.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/NEH/BTECH_CE/SEM%20VI/FarmEasy/2526_sdp8_onlineFarmerEducationAndComplaintSolvingPlatform/frontend/src/pages/Chatbot.jsx))

- `handleSendMessage` detects [.pdf](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/NEH/BTECH_CE/SEM%20VI/FarmEasy/2526_sdp8_onlineFarmerEducationAndComplaintSolvingPlatform/backend/data/raw/pdf_knowledge/crop_guides/p3.pdf) extension in attachments
- Fetches the blob URL back to a real [File](file:///c:/Users/Admin/OneDrive/Desktop/NEH/BTECH_CE/SEM%20VI/FarmEasy/2526_sdp8_onlineFarmerEducationAndComplaintSolvingPlatform/frontend/src/components/ui/multimodal-ai-chat-input.jsx#353-377) object
- `FormData` POST to `/api/chat/analyze-pdf/`
- Shows a **📄 PDF Summary** bubble with:
  - Filename + page count in header
  - `🔍 OCR` badge if vision model was used
  - ✓ High Confidence badge
  - Full structured summary text

