## 2. Inline Message Editing

### How it works

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Chatbot.jsx
    participant API as /api/chat/
    U->>UI: Hover user message → click ✏️ pencil
    UI->>UI: Replace bubble with editable textarea
    U->>UI: Edit text → "Save & Resend"
    UI->>UI: Trim messages array after edited index
    UI->>API: POST /api/chat/ with edited text + session_id
    API-->>UI: New answer + confidence + sources
    UI->>UI: Append new AI response to trimmed history
```

### State management

| State | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `editingMessageId` | ID of message being edited (`null` = not editing) |
| `editText` | Current textarea value |

### Key behaviours
- **Only user messages** get the pencil icon (not PDF upload messages)
- **Save & Resend** — truncates `messages[]` at the edited index, replaces with new user message, re-calls the RAG API
- **Cancel** or `Escape` — reverts with no changes
- `Enter` saves, `Shift+Enter` inserts newline in editor

